\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\lang2057\fs24\sl360\slmult1\qj\aspalpha 34.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\cf0\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls5\aspalpha\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang1033\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe1033\hich\f1\fs24\lang2057\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0{\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\loch\f4 The merging parties did not accept the Commission\'92s definition of the Vaal Triangle market and argued that they competed in two separate markets, Vanderbijlpark and Vereeniging. Dr Theron of Econex, who gave expert economic testimony on behalf of the mergi
