}{\rtlch\af4\ltrch\dbch\af4\hich\f4\loch\f4   This does seem to have bee
n a factor that the IDC had in mind when it decided to liquidate the company.  But it was not the only one.}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\rtlch\af1\afs20\lang1033\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe1033\hich\f1\fs20\lang2057\loch\f1\fs20\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 See evidence of Du Plessis and IDC 1 pages 146-153, IDC 3 pages 1279-1280.}}}
