 the industry as a whole is not required with a view to seeking appropriate legislative interventions.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\aspalpha\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f1\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 Some interventions of this nature, namely legislation to facilitate the conclusion of preferred provider agreement between medical schemes and hospitals are already in the pipeline, }}}
